Create and Delete Directories on Managed Node
Step 1: Create Directory
Command:
ansible local -m file -a "path=/tmp/testdir state=directory"

Step 2: Verify Directory Creation
ls -ld /tmp/testdir

Step 3: Delete Directory
Command:
ansible local -m file -a "path=/tmp/testdir state=absent"

Step 4: Verify Directory Deletion
ls -ld /tmp/testdir

